LIBRARY SERVICE UPDATE
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    In line with current Government guidance on the safe reopening
    of public buildings, Richmond upon Thames Library Service will
    begin a phased reopening from Monday 6 July 2020, starting with the
    resumption of the popular 'click and collect' service for library
    books. Please note that dates are, of course, subject to any
    further updates from Government.

