KEW ROAD BARRIERS TO BE MADE SEMI-PERMANENT
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    The recently installed water barriers on Kew Road, put in to ensure
    the mandatory cycle lane was protected from parking transgressions
    as Kew Gardens reopened, will be upgraded with to a semi-permanent
    cycle lane, now that Richmond Council has secured funds for the
    changes from Transport for London (TfL).

